{"tid":1651747,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰後檢討] 12個手足被補！次次活動都冇粉嶺唔係冇原因","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:03:16.000Z","uid":233692,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c58bf868016136211643b9d4da1c50d05562c4","tid":1651747,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"粉嶺人話你知，點解粉嶺開花=送頭<br />\n<br />\n啲人成日話粉嶺人好似住係平行世界咁，次次有活動都冇粉嶺份，本人住咗粉嶺幾年，可以同你講粉嶺真係有結界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（一）地理問題<br />\n粉嶺地理真係好差，首先粉嶺嘅交通極<strong>依賴黨鐵</strong>，同大埔太和隔住一條粉嶺公路（周邊得啲圍村），出入粉嶺嘅巴士/小巴班次都唔密，唯一係北上上水比較方便。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XzUiODw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzUiODw.jpg&h=045c68df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qw3WAjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqw3WAjw.jpg&h=c9cb4f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>地面極空曠，商場內路線簡單</strong><br />\n<br />\n（二）粉嶺真係藍到仆街<br />\n相對於上水居民因為長期受水貨客影響而偏黃，<strong>粉嶺係新移民嘅聚居地，而且好多藍血廢佬，仲要係黐線嗰隻</strong>。之前粉火對出條粉嶺橋就發生過幾單嘢，縱火燒橋、攞錘仔扑人、揼人落橋，你就知粉嶺啲藍絲幾狼死。<br />\n<br />\n今日咁多手足被送頭，其中一個原因係唔夠街坊幫拖，其二係因為呢條仆街：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pGEe6ru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpGEe6ru.jpg&h=a964ec2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真心唔想再有人送頭，粉嶺真係唔適合開花，識玩一定係出大埔沙田玩。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n反抗！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2026edefa1e8d3f830d8826899e295466b9f3c23","tid":1651747,"uid":242605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:35:53.000Z","msg":"互推<br />\n【拆炸彈 有片】懷疑 警察扮示威者 破壞車站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"efcffb79a290c172e6168a45207d258a5b349415","tid":1651747,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:36:00.000Z","msg":"推文，免送頭"},{"pid":"e9a33edcdb9e2b426c22cf7c3a3f02c4eed94e89","tid":1651747,"uid":73565,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"粉嶺人知粉嶺唔岩開花咪走去隔離區<br />\n經一事 長一智"},{"pid":"19ee9b25023b918708103fcdb9a528e52f7f7b0d","tid":1651747,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEBpKfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEBpKfS.jpg&h=ca4e0425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日記得到"},{"pid":"c05b82887d1c4f06f4db163ea5801acfd81e11b2","tid":1651747,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"推到粉嶺人見到"},{"pid":"b63ab3b424522da68d983d00020da2ccadf4fddb","tid":1651747,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"97f9132a792c6b494c74d69def3aef52478c0e42","tid":1651747,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e810fa44681351ed54d75800bc8a56dce7e9737","tid":1651747,"uid":77115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"我好早就覺得粉嶺係平行時空"},{"pid":"e4f2d12288c61672e9ad4242e5a9f8b6cf684c32","tid":1651747,"uid":162570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"我都覺,入粉嶺=送頭<br />\n唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbdfdc7efc18cc224a78388a65c33f7a8d6dc87","tid":1651747,"uid":63300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"推，粉嶺嘅地理位置真喺好難走"},{"pid":"a35d48c2f7c4acd8401db070168d30531be4cbc5","tid":1651747,"uid":112421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44a60b3f2bcf0843721e535cf4fe55c17da994a7","tid":1651747,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"960a1109e1a9b26d044082f6cb2e4bba21007c15","tid":1651747,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"推到粉嶺人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6e0ff7366dbef2dac02c4086061cd29cc246e3","tid":1651747,"uid":300387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"識玩嘅話可以直接跑上山<br />\n山上面四通八達 一定唔會畀狗捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過咁樣做 不如去上水大埔沙田好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 土生土長粉嶺鄉下佬"},{"pid":"646263b6e39c0e3b562b58c1eca3c7fe9147d651","tid":1651747,"uid":233692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"二嚟成個粉嶺分開咗兩邊，一邊係聯和墟，好多街坊都住嗰頭，但由黨鐵站入去要搭小巴或行廿幾分鐘，啲路僻不突止，中間仲要有間狗屋隔住，所以從來都冇人提出要入去開花。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊係今次手足被捕嘅地方，即由天橋連住粉火嘅粉嶺名都、粉嶺中心以及祥華邨一帶。呢幾個地方都好唔適合打游擊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">，兩個商場仔係封閉式設計，一條直路通，再加上地方細（粉嶺名都一層，粉嶺中心兩層），出到出面係空曠嘅大馬路同公園，冇地舖，冇人流，同你玩捉伊因真係易到喊。</span><br />\n<br />\n亦因為粉嶺冇中心點，冇大商場，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要聚集人群其實好難。</span>"},{"pid":"92f76806b791a6f754b8d752ba1f5db4218c6766","tid":1651747,"uid":13586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n利申：去咗上粉發夢"},{"pid":"12ffbd6ca38c50fa60e85851d10870dd5912719b","tid":1651747,"uid":1408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"住附近都覺得難走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係要散開咁走<br />\n冇得好似其他區咁大隊一齊走"},{"pid":"61e1b86a053e6491e0e52fcf0902f0285e70060a","tid":1651747,"uid":60853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:12:38.000Z","msg":"同粉嶺又有ptu同警署勁近<br />\n係粉嶺真係危險d<br />\n同廢老真係勁多"},{"pid":"87dd0c01854f7caac8e4829b3696706b9fc12872","tid":1651747,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbuF2cW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbuF2cW.png&h=b6e7be11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n合理懷疑此手足已被捕，留意佢最新post嘅強字"},{"pid":"a57abac0dd6ceed904777c2752676b0b2a4a58e5","tid":1651747,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"111a697189e496d35b0d4206905bdfcfca7aec12","tid":1651747,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70e29d76af29f5ca9de2ff6101390ad19f6e23fb","tid":1651747,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:22:32.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n推左先 分析POST"},{"pid":"a642d420f7c26c702e8e91b6ca96cded852ce91f","tid":1651747,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92f76806b791a6f754b8d752ba1f5db4218c6766","tid":1651747,"uid":13586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n利申：去咗上粉發夢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"下次唔好啦，知矛"},{"pid":"9920946a